# SMTP settings for contact form (required for real email delivery)
#
# Gmail setup for gargplywoodpalacesince1985@gmail.com:
# 1. Sign in at https://myaccount.google.com/security
# 2. Turn on 2-Step Verification (required for App Passwords)
# 3. Open https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 4. Create an App Password (name it e.g. "Garg Plywood Website")
# 5. Copy the 16-character password (no spaces) into SMTP_PASS below
# 6. Set SMTP_USER to the Gmail address that owns the App Password
# 7. Set SMTP_FROM display name; SMTP_TO is where inquiries are delivered
# 8. Save this file as .env.local and restart `npm run dev`
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=your-email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=your-app-password
SMTP_FROM="Garg Plywood Palace <gargplywoodpalacesince1985@gmail.com>"
SMTP_TO=gargplywoodpalacesince1985@gmail.com
